{"name": "streamlit-query-wrapper", "metadata": {"name": "streamlit-query-wrapper", "version": "0.1.2", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12"], "home_page": "https://github.com/minolee/streamlit_query_wrapper", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["streamlit"], "summary": "A wrapper for Streamlit components accessable via query parameters", "upload_time": 1732938304}, "documentation": ["# streamlit_query_wrapper\r\n\r\n## About\r\nThis project provides wrapper of default streamlit input widgets(checkbox, multibox, etc.).\r\n\r\nWith sharable link, you can access with exactly same setting you used.\r\n\r\n## Install\r\n`pip install streamlit-query-wrapper`\r\n\r\n## Usage\r\n\r\n```python\r\nimport streamlit_query_wrapper as stq\r\n\r\nstq.radio(\"Test\", [\"Hello\", \"world\"])\r\n\r\nstq.sharable_link() # shows st.code component with sharable URL\r\n```\r\n\r\nResult\r\n\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://github.com/minolee/streamlit_query_wrapper/blob/main/readme/basic.png?raw=true\" alt=\"drawing\"/>\r\n\r\nNow you can access your page with given link. If you access your page with given URL, all settings you made will be loaded.\r\n\r\n## Components\r\nWorks with basic streamlit input components.\r\n\r\nSupports\r\n* `checkbox`\r\n* `radio`\r\n* `selectbox`\r\n* `multiselect`\r\n* `slider`\r\n* `text_input`\r\n* `number_input`\r\n\r\nAlso works with `st.sidebar`. You can use as `stq.sidebar.checkbox` and so on.\r\n\r\nAs in original streamlit, this module uses label as default key value, and duplicate is not allowed.\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "streamlit_query_wrapper", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "streamlit_query_wrapper.query_wrapper", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "streamlit_query_wrapper.query_wrapper.SHA1", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "obj", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "streamlit_query_wrapper.query_wrapper.get_base_url", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "streamlit_query_wrapper.query_wrapper.sharable_link", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Full URL including base url and all query wrapper key-value pairs"]}, {"name": "streamlit_query_wrapper.query_wrapper.sharable_part", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["URL part including all query wrapper key-value pairs. This does not include base url"]}, {"name": "streamlit_query_wrapper.query_wrapper.map_positional_arg_to_keyword_args", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "module", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "*args", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "streamlit_query_wrapper.query_wrapper.load_value_from_query", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "query", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "hash_table", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "streamlit_query_wrapper.query_wrapper.load_hash_table", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "items", "type": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "streamlit_query_wrapper.query_wrapper.should_use_hash", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "value", "type": {"name": "